            <div class="[font-weight:500;]">
              4 sessions<span class="label-text-alt text-sm">/month</span>
              {"->"} ${50 * 4}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
    <div class="divider divider-vertical mx-auto my-7 mt-10 w-2/3"></div>
    <div class="mb-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
      <div>
        <h1 class="mb-5 mt-3 font-sans text-5xl font-black">Pricing FAQ</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="max-w-prose">
        Distinctio et nulla eum soluta et neque labore quibusdam. Saepe et quasi
        iusto modi velit ut non voluptas in. Explicabo id ut laborum.
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
